snippet.title: Super Bust-A-Move (PS2 Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Super Bust-A-Move (PS2) - Player: Mog - Mode: Normal

BUST into a world of bubble-bursting puzzle-popping fun! Unlock secret characters, rescue captives and more. Conveyor belts challenge your Super BAM skills. Mind blowing, puzzle-packed addictive gameplay. Match bubble-breaking wits with a friend in 2 player Battle mode.
